'''小沙鼠屬'''（學名'''''Gerbillus'''''）是[[沙鼠|沙鼠]]中的一[[屬|屬]]，在某些文獻當中，''Dipodillus'' 與''Microdillus''兩屬，也被歸類為本屬。

==物種==
*''Hendecapleura''亞屬
**''Gerbillus amoenus''
**''Gerbillus brockmani''
**''Gerbillus famulus''
**''Gerbillus garamantis''
**''Gerbillus grobbeni''
**''Gerbillus henleyi''
**''Gerbillus mauritaniae'' （有時被單列為一屬）
**''Gerbillus mesopotamiae''
**''Gerbillus muriculus''
**''Gerbillus nanus''
**''Gerbillus poecilops''
**''Gerbillus principulus''
**''Gerbillus pusillus''
**''Gerbillus syrticus''
**''Gerbillus vivax''
**''Gerbillus watersi'' 
*''Gerbillus''亞屬
**''Gerbillus acticola''
**''Gerbillus agag''
**''Gerbillus andersoni''
**''Gerbillus aquilus''
**''Gerbillus burtoni''
**''Gerbillus cheesmani''
**''Gerbillus dongolanus''
**''Gerbillus dunni''
**''Gerbillus floweri''
**''Gerbillus gerbillus''
**''Gerbillus gleadowi''
**''Gerbillus hesperinus''
**''Gerbillus hoogstraali''
**''Gerbillus latastei''
**''Gerbillus nancillus''
**''Gerbillus nigeriae''
**''Gerbillus occiduus''
**''Gerbillus perpallidus''
**''Gerbillus pulvinatus''
**''Gerbillus pyramidum''
**''Gerbillus rosalinda''
**''Gerbillus tarabuli''

